===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} {{figure of speech}} The use of a word or phrase to refer to something that it isn't, invoking a direct similarity between the word or phrase used and the thing described, and without the words "like" or "as".
# {{countable}} The word or phrase used in this way.  An implied comparison.

